    "heading" : "Key Risks",
    "body" : "1. Re-acceleration of US inflation forcing the Fed to pivot hawkish (probability 15 %). 2. China hard landing spilling into global supply chains (probability 20 %). 3. Geopolitical escalation in the Middle East lifting energy prices > $100/bbl (probability 12 %). 4. US fiscal deterioration triggering a term-premium spike above 200 bp (probability 18 %)."
